body:
@sahilTakiar thanks for the nice summary of MkDocs & RTD. I never got around to documenting my own findings. Great someone else did that for me.
In my own project I resorted to CSS and JavaScript trickery to fix some of the issues. I also added an in-page TOC on-the-fly with JavaScript: http://nodemcu.readthedocs.org/en/dev/en/modules/mqtt/. 

Two issues I believe you missed are https://github.com/rtfd/readthedocs.org/issues/1917 (broken fly-out menu links) and https://github.com/mkdocs/mkdocs/issues/269 ("Edit on GitHub" links sub-par).
